<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
  <title>500 - Server Error - UnfilteredFaiz</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300..900;1,9..144,300..900&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      background-color: #0c0f1a;
      color: #f1f5f9;
      touch-action: pan-x pan-y;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent !important;
      -webkit-user-select: none;
      user-select: none;
    }
    
    .error-container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      width: 90%;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
      gap: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    
    .error-content {
      padding: 4rem 3.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .error-code {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 6rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c4a882, #e5d5c0);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
    }
    
    .error-title {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      color: #f8fafc;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    
    .error-text {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .error-btn {
      align-self: flex-start;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      background-color: #c4a882;
      color: #0c0f1a;
      padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      border: 1px solid #c4a882;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(196, 168, 130, 0.15);
      -webkit-user-select: text;
      user-select: text;
    }
    
    .error-btn:hover {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: #c4a882;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(196, 168, 130, 0.25);
    }
    
    .error-visual {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 480px;
    }
    
    .error-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      transition: transform 10s ease;
    }
    
    .error-visual:hover .error-img {
      transform: scale(1.08);
    }
    
    .error-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(12, 15, 26, 0.95) 0%, rgba(12, 15, 26, 0.4) 30%, transparent 100%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .error-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        max-width: 550px;
      }
      
      .error-content {
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        order: 2;
      }
      
      .error-visual {
        min-height: 280px;
        order: 1;
      }
      
      .error-overlay {
        background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(12, 15, 26, 0.95) 0%, rgba(12, 15, 26, 0.3) 50%, transparent 100%);
      }
      
      .error-code {
        font-size: 4.5rem;
      }
      
      .error-title {
        font-size: 1.85rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <div class="error-content">
      <div class="error-code">500</div>
      <h1 class="error-title">Lost in the mist.</h1>
      <p class="error-text">
        Our servers encountered an unexpected storm while trying to load this page. Just like a climber facing dense fog, we're currently finding our bearings.
      </p>
      <a href="/home" class="error-btn">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline></svg>
        Return to Home
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="error-visual">
      <img src="/images/error-500.jpg" alt="Mountain summit sunrise" class="error-img">
      <div class="error-overlay"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
